{"tid":1294294,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［集思廣益］今時今日司法覆核可唔可以制裁警犬","createTime":"2019-07-07T18:13:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T03:41:01.000Z","uid":21961,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"91a4d707fe063adef92530f40d914b8794ac5ccb","tid":1294294,"uid":21961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T18:13:52.000Z","msg":"第一，今日係旺角食完飯嘅巴打，落樓嘅時候受到暴力對待，甚至有警犬唔帶證，違反警察通例。<br />\n<br />\n第二，記者朋友今晚採訪明顯受阻，警犬有意妨礙新聞自由，封鎖線入面唔比記者入。<br />\n<br />\n今時今日律師同堂費我地都有，雖然司法覆核時間長程序多，未必有即時功效，但長遠計算係有效手段？（監警會廢 又用唔到權力法去查）<br />\n<br />\n有冇法律巴打研究下"},{"pid":"38935a6e090f16bef88bf92306de13e0f8b70aed","tid":1294294,"uid":35831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T18:15:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ed032347b0aaa2be7fa84a3e4914386147e75b29","tid":1294294,"uid":160605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T18:16:31.000Z","msg":"冇委任證吹佢唔漲...但連制服連背心都冇可以釘死佢"},{"pid":"e1961e4e961ab9e2cb4cbf5b0eadc23022209f45","tid":1294294,"uid":83477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T18:17:34.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"33802880338b9704888d69471934fc08de1779ca","tid":1294294,"uid":98520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T18:19:08.000Z","msg":"其實班警係欺善怕惡,根本無野可以令到佢地覺得驚,橫行霸道,目中無人<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1294279\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1294279</a>"},{"pid":"754313470f23d12044431d8ac6b81873815e1324","tid":1294294,"uid":21961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T18:41:31.000Z","msg":"Push <br />\n <br />\nI have the right to remain silenced."},{"pid":"984c74c3b0c3020640027ebbc0253935379ba936","tid":1294294,"uid":14921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T19:03:21.000Z","msg":"<code>Push 我無嘢講 我要見律師 我唔解鎖電話 我唔簽任何文件 我要去醫院驗傷</code>"},{"pid":"9164a95eae3f47c81a2305cc58c040d25d3d71fa","tid":1294294,"uid":35831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":